# TPDS Application Root

This project holds the main navigation and documentation for the Trust Platform Design Suite

## Release Notes

### 2.4.2
   - Switch function added to show Legacy Configurator if installed
   - Cleaned up SDE User guide links

### 2.4.1
   - Manifest generation and parser updates for lite and larger key types

### 2.4.0
   - Improved Usecase UI for migrating from Notebook based Usecases to native React and Python based
   - ECC608 TFLXTLS Configurator updates for extended certificate expire years support

### 2.3.13
   - Secure Exchange Process form updates for Computing Products and MoQ details
   - Other improvements and bug fixes like cert options for ECC Configurator, Reopening the Usecase

### 2.3.x
   - Learning Center links update and UI adjustment to screen
   - pypi links to Package names under Package Manager to access Release notes
